nodes.text: Coruscant and the Core Worlds is a sourcebook for the Star Wars Roleplaying Game published by Wizards of the Coast on January 3, 2003.

The book covers historical and major character information related to 28 planets of the Core Worlds, as well as one space station. A web enhancement titled J't'p'tan: Temples and Tybis was later released on Wizards of the Coast's website.
